Entries.default: "A marvel. I could spend days studying this. I... don't suppose that's the plan?"
"Belfetto! What an extraordinary machine. It is a shame this has been hidden here for all this time."
"That device... a mechanical Eora, I say."
"Ishi, fly up there and crack open one of those bronze eggs."
"Watcher, ask them if they got a model depicting Hel."
"Remaro'd be half hard at the sight of this. Weren't a star he didn't know to sail by."
